{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1506,"text":"When I arrived in Kiev,"},{"time":3335,"text":"on February 1 this year,"},{"time":5731,"text":"Independence Square was under siege,"},{"time":8350,"text":"surrounded by police\nloyal to the government."},{"time":11988,"text":"The protesters who occupied Maidan,"},{"time":14529,"text":"as the square is known,"},{"time":16361,"text":"prepared for battle,"},{"time":17981,"text":"stockpiling homemade weapons"},{"time":20240,"text":"and mass-producing improvised body armor."},{"time":24160,"text":"The Euromaidan protests began peacefully\nat the end of 2013,"},{"time":29133,"text":"after the president of Ukraine,\nViktor Yanukovych,"},{"time":32364,"text":"rejected a far-reaching accord\nwith the European Union"},{"time":35850,"text":"in favor of stronger ties with Russia."},{"time":38847,"text":"In response, tens of thousands\nof dissatisfied citizens"},{"time":42204,"text":"poured into central Kiev\nto demonstrate against this allegiance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47656,"text":"As the months passed,"},{"time":49291,"text":"confrontations between police\nand civilians intensified."},{"time":53858,"text":"I set up a makeshift portrait studio\nby the barricades on Hrushevsky Street."},{"time":60248,"text":"There, I photographed\nthe fighters against a black curtain,"},{"time":64551,"text":"a curtain that obscured\nthe highly seductive and visual backdrop"},{"time":68949,"text":"of fire, ice and smoke."},{"time":72858,"text":"In order to tell the individual\nhuman stories here,"},{"time":76242,"text":"I felt that I needed to remove\nthe dramatic visuals"},{"time":79376,"text":"that had become so familiar and repetitive\nwithin the mainstream media."},{"time":84455,"text":"What I was witnessing\nwas not only news, but also history."},{"time":88593,"text":"With this realization,"},{"time":89928,"text":"I was free from\nthe photojournalistic conventions"},{"time":92864,"text":"of the newspaper and the magazine."},{"time":95869,"text":"Oleg, Vasiliy and Maxim\nwere all ordinary men,"},{"time":100895,"text":"with ordinary lives from ordinary towns."},{"time":104309,"text":"But the elaborate costumes\nthat they had bedecked themselves in"},{"time":107623,"text":"were quite extraordinary."},{"time":108953,"text":"I say the word \"costume\""},{"time":110744,"text":"because these were not clothes\nthat had been issued"},{"time":113194,"text":"or coordinated by anyone."},{"time":115179,"text":"They were improvised uniforms"},{"time":117483,"text":"made up of decommissioned\nmilitary equipment,"},{"time":120363,"text":"irregular combat fatigues\nand trophies taken from the police."},{"time":125725,"text":"I became interested in the way they\nwere choosing to represent themselves,"},{"time":130297,"text":"this outward expression of masculinity,"},{"time":133843,"text":"the ideal of the warrior."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136724,"text":"I worked slowly,\nusing an analog film camera"},{"time":140009,"text":"with a manual focusing loop\nand a handheld light meter."},{"time":143764,"text":"The process is old-fashioned."},{"time":146279,"text":"It gives me time to speak with each person"},{"time":149268,"text":"and to look at them, in silence,\nwhile they look back at me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155755,"text":"Rising tensions culminated\nin the worst day of violence"},{"time":158982,"text":"on February 20,"},{"time":160711,"text":"which became known as Bloody Thursday."},{"time":163663,"text":"Snipers, loyal to the government,"},{"time":165717,"text":"started firing on the civilians\nand protesters on Institutskaya Street."},{"time":171120,"text":"Many were killed\nin a very short space of time."},{"time":175123,"text":"The reception of the Hotel Ukraine\nbecame a makeshift morgue."},{"time":179236,"text":"There were lines\nof bodies laid in the street."},{"time":182282,"text":"And there was blood\nall over the pavements."},{"time":185908,"text":"The following day,\nPresident Yanukovych fled Ukraine."},{"time":190146,"text":"In all, three months of protests"},{"time":191929,"text":"resulted in more than 120 confirmed dead"},{"time":195398,"text":"and many more missing."},{"time":197913,"text":"History unfolded quickly,"},{"time":199956,"text":"but celebration remained\nelusive in Maidan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203488,"text":"As the days passed\nin Kiev's central square,"},{"time":206289,"text":"streams of armed fighters"},{"time":207828,"text":"were joined by tens of thousands\nof ordinary people,"},{"time":211254,"text":"filling the streets in an act\nof collective mourning."},{"time":215174,"text":"Many were women who often carried flowers"},{"time":217588,"text":"that they had brought to lay\nas marks of respect for the dead."},{"time":221768,"text":"They came day after day"},{"time":223339,"text":"and they covered the square\nwith millions of flowers."},{"time":228517,"text":"Sadness enveloped Maidan."},{"time":231281,"text":"It was quiet and I could hear\nthe birds singing."},{"time":233895,"text":"I hadn't heard that before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236141,"text":"I stopped women\nas they approached the barricades"},{"time":238639,"text":"to lay their tributes"},{"time":239807,"text":"and asked to make their picture."},{"time":242478,"text":"Most women cried when I photographed them."},{"time":245592,"text":"On the first day,\nmy fixer, Emine, and I cried"},{"time":247768,"text":"with almost every woman\nwho visited our studio."},{"time":252876,"text":"There had been such a noticeable\nabsence of women"},{"time":255882,"text":"up until that point."},{"time":257625,"text":"And the color of their pastel coats,"},{"time":259918,"text":"their shiny handbags,"},{"time":261656,"text":"and the bunches of red carnations,"},{"time":263746,"text":"white tulips and yellow roses\nthat they carried"},{"time":266977,"text":"jarred with the blackened square"},{"time":269113,"text":"and the blackened men\nwho were encamped there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273105,"text":"It is clear to me\nthat these two sets of pictures"},{"time":275956,"text":"don't make much sense without the other."},{"time":278694,"text":"They are about men and women\nand the way we are --"},{"time":281091,"text":"not the way we look,\nbut the way we are."},{"time":283831,"text":"They speak about different\ngender roles in conflict,"},{"time":286663,"text":"not only in Maidan,\nand not only in Ukraine."},{"time":290597,"text":"Men fight most wars and women mourn them."},{"time":294399,"text":"If the men showed\nthe ideal of the warrior,"},{"time":296835,"text":"then the women showed\nthe implications of such violence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301256,"text":"When I made these pictures,"},{"time":303020,"text":"I believed that I was documenting\nthe end of violent events in Ukraine."},{"time":306824,"text":"But now I understand\nthat it is a record of the beginning."},{"time":310317,"text":"Today, the death toll stands around 3,000,"},{"time":313730,"text":"while hundreds of thousands\nhave been displaced."},{"time":317847,"text":"I was in Ukraine again six weeks ago."},{"time":320547,"text":"In Maidan, the barricades\nhave been dismantled,"},{"time":324035,"text":"and the paving stones which were used\nas weapons during the protests replaced,"},{"time":327917,"text":"so that traffic flows freely\nthrough the center of the square."},{"time":332129,"text":"The fighters, the women\nand the flowers are gone."},{"time":336737,"text":"A huge billboard depicting geese\nflying over a wheat field"},{"time":340538,"text":"covers the burned-out shell\nof the trade union's building"},{"time":343806,"text":"and proclaims,"},{"time":345234,"text":"\"Glory to Ukraine."},{"time":346685,"text":"Glory to heroes.\""},{"time":348383,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":349383,"text":"(Applause)."}]}]}